<title>ạ̉nt ạlmlk yạ yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̹nt ạlmlk yạ yswʿ .. wmyn gẖyrk ymlk
 ạ̹nt ạldwạ yạ yswʿ .. wmyn gẖyrk ysẖfy)2
