 frḥk fạḍ wmlạny .. kẖly̱ ḥyạty tgẖny)2
 2- (rwḥk sạkn fynạ .. ḥbk bydfynạ
 ṣwtk byʿzynạ .. ạmlk fy wsṭynạ)2</lyrics>
